- Components should be in the components/ directory
- Pages should be in the pages/ directory
- Styles should be in the scss/ directory
- Utility functions should be in the utils/ directory
- Custom hooks should be in the hooks/ directory
- Each component should have its own directory with:
  - index.tsx
  - styles.module.scss
  - component-name.test.tsx
- Keep related files close together
- Use index files for clean exports
- Always use lowercase-kabab-case for filenames. Never use capital letters.
